<br>
This is a great zone to either group or solo in my opinion. I'm currently soloing the Skeletal Brigands, Lesser Shades, and a variety of Rockhoppers.  The rockhoppers drop the HQ hides used in a variety of quests the Vah Shir do so they are a great way to supplement your bank (avg price is 10pp per hide!).<br>
<br>
From Level 10 through Level 14 I believe you can hunt the Lodi Kai bandits/brigands as they con yellow/white to me at this level.<br>
<br>
I've tried my air, fire and water pet and the one that seems to be most effective at this point is the water pet.  I haven't tried the earth pet yet because some types of the rockhoppers do have a poison attack which does like 12 damage per round.<br>
<br>
And I just want to say, that I'm getting great comments on the way Verant changed the images of our pets!  Just for kicks, I parked my pet outside the bank there in Shadeweaver's, and then I ran around behind the bank.  People thought that my pet was an npc at first!  Well, until I did the /pet who leader command.. hee hee....<br>
<br>
But definitely give this place a look at.  Lots of nice things to hunt and great people to be met.<br>
<br>
Faal<br>
9th Mage<br>
